channel.title: Two quick questions i need help with
channel.description:
I'm running a server and their are too many admins and I lost count of who is... I just want to demote them all... In my data folder, there is a thing that says administrators but that is no good it is just blank.
In another question, how do I make an undercover for my default account? I saw this in a tutorial but I lost it.

item.title: Two quick questions i need help with
item.dc:creator: @jc22493 Jc22493
item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

You could try to remember who you made administrator.

And if you want to make so many people administrators, you should write down their names somewhere so you don’t forget.
